name: Magnussen_D2471_Karlin_Wood_Round_Dining_Table_with_Wood_Top
reviews: This was the worst decision i made. The base of this table chips every time it comes in contact with a chair leg and that is every time a chair is pushed under the table. Under the simulated wood paint is a yellow plastic material. I have yet to figure out how i am going to hide this. Save yourself and spend the money to get something made of real wood or at least has a better finish.
It is the perfect ash color and gorgeous finish. A lot of show for little money!
description:
Bring old-world charm to your home with this round dining table. Constructed of hardwood solids and supported by a sturdy base, this indoor dining table is ready for any occasion. The dry-gray acacia finish along with the glass and pewter hardware make this piece a wonderful addition to any dining room or breakfast nook.
